# CHANGELOG Maintenance

Update `CHANGELOG.md` when adding, changing, or removing functionality.

## Format

Follow [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/) conventions:

```markdown
## [Unreleased]

### Added
- New feature description

### Changed
- Existing feature modification

### Fixed
- Bug fix description

### Removed
- Removed feature description

## [v1.2.0] - 2026-03-09

### Added
- ...
```

## Rules

- New entries go under `[Unreleased]` until a version tag is pushed
- When releasing, rename `[Unreleased]` to `[vX.Y.Z] - YYYY-MM-DD` and add a fresh `[Unreleased]` section
- Write entries from the user's perspective, not implementation details
- Group related changes under one bullet rather than listing every file touched
- Reference GitHub issue/PR numbers where applicable
